        <h3>‚öîÔ∏è Roles</h3>
        <p>At the start of each game, players are randomly assigned one of two roles:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><b>The Infected</b> ‚Äî try to overwhelm your opponent with aggressive tactics.</li>
            <li><b>The Survivor</b> ‚Äî hold your ground, defend, and outlast.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Your role determines the cards in your deck and your playstyle.</p>

        <h3>üÉè Card Types</h3>
