            <li><b>Combat Cards</b> ‚Äî have Attack and Defense values. Played using Energy.</li>
            <li><b>Leader Cards</b> ‚Äî rare draws from the deck that give permanent attack or defense bonuses.</li>
            <li><b>Spell Cards (coming soon)</b> ‚Äî powerful effects that can shift the tide of battle.</li>

        </ul>

        <h3>‚ö° Energy & Health</h3>
        <p>Each turn, you gain energy to play cards.</p>
        <p>To see your or your opponent‚Äôs health and energy, hover over the avatar.</p>

        <h3>‚è±Ô∏è Turn Rules</h3>

        <p>You have 30 seconds to take your turn.</p>
        <p>During your turn:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Play combat cards by spending energy.</li>
            <li>When the turn ends, all cards attack and defend simultaneously.</li>
            <li>If a card receives more damage than its defense, the excess damage hits the player directly.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>‚ò†Ô∏è Defeat</h3>
